AOI NIGHT RESTRICTIONS:
AMEND TO READ:
NO TKOF/LDG BETWEEN 2100-0500++.
EXCEPTIONS FOR COMMERCIAL PASSENGER TFC:
- TKOF/LDG BETWEEN 2100-2230+ AND 0430-0500++;
- EARLY LDG BETWEEN 0400-0430+ IF PLANNED TIME OF
ARR IS AFTER 0430++;
- DELAYED TKOF/LDG BETWEEN 2230-2300+ IF PLANNED TIME OF
DEP/ARR IS BEFORE 2230++;
ABOVE MENTIONED RESTRICTIONS DO NOT APPLY TO:
- FLTS OF MISSIONS OF AID IN CASE OF EMERG AND CATASTROPHE;
- FLTS FOR MEDICAL SUPPLIES AND HUMANITARIAN FLTS;
- LDGS DUE TO MET, TECHNICAL OR OTHER SAFETY REASONS;
- MIL REQUIREMENTS;
- PPR FOR INDIVIDUAL CASES.
